org.sbml.squeezer
Class UnitFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.sbml.squeezer.UnitFactory

public class UnitFactory
extends Object

A factory class that creates frequently used instances of Unit and UnitDefinition if these are not yet present in a Model. To this end, it always checks the Model and tries to obtain existing UnitDefinitions from the Model whenever this is possible.
